OL,3,CHealthcare assistant admits neglect
OL,4,Cafter death of teenager
OL,6,FA healthcare assistant has pleaded
OL,7,Fguilty to wilful neglect after the
OL,8,Fdeath of a teenage patient at a mental
OL,9,Fhealth hospital in Nottingham.
OL,11,FSylvia Quaye-Mensah, 42, changed her
OL,12,Fplea on what would have been the first
OL,13,Fday of her trial at Nottingham Crown
OL,14,FCourt.
OL,16,FThe defendant, of Monsall Avenue in
OL,17,FIlkeston, Derbyshire, admitted ill-
OL,18,Ftreatment or neglect by a care worker
OL,19,F"by failing to undertake required
OL,20,Fobservations" of 19-year-old Louise
OL,21,FFurlong.
