OL,3,CHealthcare assistant admits neglect
OL,4,Cafter death of teenager
OL,6,FMs Furlong died at Highbury Hospital
OL,7,Fin Bulwell on September 12 2022 the
OL,8,Fday after an incident happened.
OL,10,FThe exact nature of the incident has
OL,11,Fnot been confirmed.
OL,13,FQuaye-Mensah, who stood in the dock
OL,14,Fwearing a grey zipped jacket over a
OL,15,Fblack top, was told she will be
OL,16,Fsentenced on March 2 next year, and
OL,17,Fwas granted conditional bail until
OL,18,Fthen.
